result.name: Tsui Wah Restaurant

reviews.text: This is my favorite of all the Tsui Wah Restaurants in Hong Kong. It is the place to hate by most locals. Prices are higher than most other diners and the food leans a little too western for most locals. It is a cross between western and a Hong Kong  Diner. Lots of good memories here for me with shared meals with Eddie and lessons learned on Hong Kong etiquette. If you are sitting alone at a table for two, someone you don't know will sit down at your table and this is acceptable. Time and space is money in Hong Kong and once you get use to it you will start to appreciate it.

Stopped by for a fresh-out-of-oven pineapple bun and the red bean pineapple bun.  Both are awesome and I can have these evil buns everyday!  Aside these buns, dine in experience is not bad either, with a vast selection for breakfast, lunch and dinner, sure you'll find something that goes along with your taste bus.

The waters are very impatient and impolite. The price is acceptable cuz it's in Central. The food quality doesn't quite match the price tag. Overall, I won't consider this restaurant if there are other choices.

Good food, good prices. Definitely recommend.
We came here for Afternoon Tea (2:30-6:00pm). Pictures attached :)

Me and my friend having late dinner here at Tsui wah Restaurant in Tsim Sha Tsui Mtr exit D2 or D1.. waitress are approachable.. food are 🎶good and homie 😁we order beef brisket rice noodles and lemon tea

result.name: 翠華餐廳

reviews.text: 服務員態度很好👍

This is my favorite of all the Tsui Wah Restaurants in Hong Kong. It is the place to hate by most locals. Prices are higher than most other diners and the food leans a little too western for most locals. It is a cross between western and a Hong Kong  Diner. Lots of good memories here for me with shared meals with Eddie and lessons learned on Hong Kong etiquette. If you are sitting alone at a table for two, someone you don't know will sit down at your table and this is acceptable. Time and space is money in Hong Kong and once you get use to it you will start to appreciate it.
味道一般，服務態度也是一般通病流程，價格徧高些，略為低些更妤，整體而言尚可一去！

好吃，开到2am。云吞和牛腩面还有那汤太好吃了。服务员很友善，真的，谈得很开心，吃也吃的很幸福。过后因为我是旅客迷了路，有一位服务员还带我走到我旅馆的街上。心地善良，赞！Great place for late night food, opens to 2am. Absolutely divine local wanton and other dishes. I found the staff very friendly and we were chatting away. As I'm a tourist and lost, one old staff even walked me to my hotel street. Love it!
食物水準比兩三年前大幅下降，目標顧客主要是不會翻頭的內地旅客。
